      "type": "rich-text",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "YOU",
        "rich_text": "<p>We believe in creating clothing that resonates with your unique identity and style. Designed for individuals with a strong belief in tradition, yet possessing a progressive outlook. Our collection is tailored to compliment and enhance your lifestyle offering a sophisticated wardrobe that speaks to your refined sense. Whether you are dressing for a professional outing, a sophisticated event, our garments ensure that you are always impeccably dressed. Modern, Heritage and You is a convergence for contemporary design, traditional craft and personal expression.</p>",
